Class Description

ApiPackageOverviewTypeEnum
Enum describing the type of a Pojo
ApiPojoElement
Model for displaying a Pojo on the index page
AttributeRs
AttributeRs describes a attribute relationship between a PojoClass and PojoClass, PojoReference or PojoInterface
BinaryReading
Contains functions for reading java class files and converting them into ASM ClassNodes
BinaryReadingException
Exception during binary reading process
ClassHandlingException
Exception type for errors during the reading of Pojos from ASM ClassNodes.

ErrorMessage
Model for displaying a error message to the user
ExceptionHandlingController
Controller for exception handling
ExportFormat
Model for JSON export of all Pojos in the database
ExtendsRs
ExtendsRs describes an inheritance relationship between a PojoClass and another PojoClass or PojoReference
FileUploadController
Controller for uploading Pojos as a JAR or class file.
ImplementsRs
ImplementsRs describes a relationship between a PojoClass and a PojoInterface, which the PojoClass implements
ImportExportController
Controller for importing or exporting Pojos in JSON format
ImportExportService
ImportExportService adds Pojos from JSON file to the database and exports Pojos from the database
IndexController
Controller for the index page of the application
IndexService
IndexService provides the index page, which has an overview of all Pojos in the database
JsonUtils
Utils for handling of JSON data
PackageOverviewController
Controller for receiving an overview over the contents of a package
PackageOverviewService
PackageOverviewService provides a list of all Pojos in a given package, including subpackages of the same package
PojoApplication
Entry point of the SpringBoot project
PojoAttributeController
Controller for manually add and deleting attributes of a Pojo
PojoAttributeService
PojoAttributeService manages adding and removing attributes to and from Pojos
PojoClass
PojoClass represents a standard java class
PojoClassRepository
Neo4j repository for Objects of type PojoClass
PojoDeleteController
Controller for deleting Pojos
PojoDeleteService
PojoDeleteService manages the deletion of all or single Pojos
PojoElement
PojoElement is the base class for all POJO classes
PojoElementRepository
Neo4j repository for Objects of type PojoElement
PojoInterface
PojoInterface represents a java interface.
PojoInterfaceRepository
Neo4j repository for Objects of type PojoInterface
PojoReference
PojoReference represents a standard java class that was added to the database without its bytecode, either manually or through referencing in another Pojo
PojoReferenceRepository
Neo4j repository for Objects of type PojoReference
PojoStatistic
Model for statistical information about a Pojo
RedirectPageContentService
Produces html page that automatically redirects to index page
StatisticController
Controller for receiving statistical information about a Pojo
StatisticService
StatisticService retrieves statistical information about a given Pojo from the database
Swagger2Config
Swagger Configuration This class represents the configuration for the swagger plugin.
